{"word":"Bilhah","slug":"bilhah","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Bilhah</b> <a href=\"#/H1090\">H1090</a> <br/> 1. Rachel's servant<br/> - Bears children by Jacob<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=29&verse=29'>Gen 29:29</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=30&verse=4'>Gen 30:4</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=37&verse=2'>Gen 37:2</a> <br/> - Mother of Dan and Naphtali<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=30&verse=8'>Gen 30:8</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=35&verse=25'>Gen 35:25</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=46&verse=25'>Gen 46:25</a> <br/> - Reuben's incest with<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=35&verse=22'>Gen 35:22</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=49&verse=4'>Gen 49:4</a> <br/> 2. A place in the land of Simeon<br/> - General references<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=4&verse=29'>1Ch 4:29</a> <br/> - Called Balah<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=6&chapter=19&verse=3'>Jos 19:3</a> <br/> - Called Baalah<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=6&chapter=15&verse=29'>Jos 15:29</a> "}]}